1
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:13,120
Listen to me

2
00:01:13,320 --> 00:01:14,400
Everything you just did

3
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:15,440
is against the law

4
00:01:15,440 --> 00:01:16,800
I could call the cops on you

5
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:18,560
Shut your mouth, little girl

6
00:01:20,720 --> 00:01:21,520
Old fossil

7
00:01:22,720 --> 00:01:25,320
If I don't set you straight today

8
00:01:28,440 --> 00:01:30,080
you'll never learn your lesson

9
00:01:33,440 --> 00:01:34,320
What are you doing?

10
00:01:40,320 --> 00:01:40,920
Oh no

11
00:01:42,480 --> 00:01:43,760
It must be the previous agent

12
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:45,640
Lin You

13
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:47,400
I'll head down first

14
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:48,240
You call the police

15
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:50,320
Old fossil

16
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:51,520
I'll teach you to burn paper! Hello, 110?

17
00:01:51,520 --> 00:01:52,680
Hands off Grandma! Someone broke in here!

18
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:53,840
I'll beat you deaf! Let go of Grandma!

19
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:55,120
Building 3, No. 28, Xingfu Road

20
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:56,240
Okay, okay

21
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:57,480
Please hurry!

22
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:58,520
Lin You!

23
00:01:58,760 --> 00:01:59,520
Let her go! Help!

24
00:01:59,520 --> 00:02:00,480
Lin You, stop!

25
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:01,280
Who are you?

26
00:02:02,080 --> 00:02:03,280
Lin You, the cops are on their way

27
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:04,400
Lin You, are you alright?

28
00:02:08,720 --> 00:02:09,320
You...

29
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,040
Bro You

30
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,000
You're out now

31
00:02:16,920 --> 00:02:18,680
I didn't know this job involved you

32
00:02:19,040 --> 00:02:20,120
We're all on the same side

33
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:21,920
Same side?

34
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,240
Who's on your side?

35
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:25,440
You bastard

36
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:26,720
Bro You

37
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:29,080
We all work for Bro Chen

38
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:31,640
This doesn't look good for any of us

39
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,440
I'll remember this

40
00:02:34,040 --> 00:02:34,720
Old lady

41
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:37,000
They aren't good people either

42
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:37,720
I don't believe

43
00:02:37,720 --> 00:02:39,280
they can protect you 24 hours a day

44
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:40,080
Just you wait

45
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:42,200
It's okay

46
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:47,960
Are you okay, Lin You?

47
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:53,320
Grandma

48
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:54,640
Grandma

49
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:56,040
Grandma, what's wrong?

50
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:57,960
Grandma, wake up! Grandma!

51
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:59,160
Grandma! Grandma!

52
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:20,960
No way

53
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:23,640
We need to control that little thing

54
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:43,240
Primordial Sovereign's True Breath

55
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:45,600
Merge with my being

56
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:48,600
Where the Heavenly Dipper points

57
00:03:48,720 --> 00:03:50,960
Day and night forever turn

58
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:54,680
A humble mortal of this world

59
00:03:54,920 --> 00:03:57,280
Seeks the Way and prays for the divine

60
00:03:57,680 --> 00:04:00,120
May I behold your sacred form

61
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:02,720
To forever guard eternal life

62
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:21,800
Kui, Wei, Yu, Piao, Honored Emperor

63
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,240
By the urgent decree!

64
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:23,880
Freeze!

65
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:31,760
Boundless Heavenly Lord of Life

66
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,680
Up in the middle of the night

67
00:04:35,080 --> 00:04:36,360
disturbing a little kid

68
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:39,960
People these days have no manners

69
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:42,200
Old Wang

70
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:44,720
Master

71
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:46,400
You're finally back

72
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,200
Come here

73
00:04:53,880 --> 00:04:55,560
You little brat

74
00:04:55,640 --> 00:04:56,760
If it weren't for your good luck

75
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:57,920
I'm telling you

76
00:04:58,720 --> 00:05:00,480
without the old lady's amulet

77
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:01,640
you'd all be done for

78
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:03,680
Amulet?

79
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,440
How come I never saw it?

80
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:07,880
The one you photographed for me

81
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:10,400
The old lady is truly thoughtful

82
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:11,800
Otherwise

83
00:05:12,200 --> 00:05:13,160
what would you have done?

84
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:21,360
Lin You

85
00:05:21,440 --> 00:05:22,000
How are you?

86
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:22,640
You okay?

87
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:23,320
I'm fine

88
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:24,200
Where's Grandma Sun?

89
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,920
Grandma's feeling better now

90
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:28,960
She was probably just startled

91
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:32,160
Oh, right

92
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:35,200
Grandma Sun gave me this before it happened

93
00:05:54,280 --> 00:05:55,080
Grandma

94
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:57,000
I'm having a baby

95
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,400
Came to share the good news with you

96
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:08,640
Wonderful

97
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:13,920
Three years ago

98
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:16,240
The ones living in Xiaobai's place

99
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:17,960
were a young couple renting it

100
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:19,480
They were very kind

101
00:06:19,840 --> 00:06:21,080
The only ones in that building

102
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:23,120
willing to get close to Grandma Sun

103
00:06:41,440 --> 00:06:42,520
And Grandma

104
00:06:42,520 --> 00:06:44,560
would make little clothes for the baby

105
00:06:44,960 --> 00:06:47,040
Xiaohuang would often visit Grandma too

106
00:06:47,520 --> 00:06:48,960
chatting with her

107
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,200
basking in the sun

108
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:52,240
Be a good baby

109
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:54,080
This is Great-Grandma

110
00:06:57,760 --> 00:07:00,360
Two strangers with no blood relation

111
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:01,640
just like that

112
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:04,320
became family to each other

113
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:13,040
Until one day

114
00:07:13,320 --> 00:07:15,320
something happened to Xiaohuang's baby

115
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:18,200
Grandma could only stand by the window

116
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:20,480
watching the ambulance take her away

117
00:07:28,200 --> 00:07:29,440
After that

118
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:32,680
Grandma Sun never saw them again

119
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:35,720
So

120
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,800
we have to help Grandma Sun even more

121
00:07:38,960 --> 00:07:39,760
But

122
00:07:40,400 --> 00:07:43,240
Why is Grandma Sun bothering Xiaobai?

123
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:45,960
According to Grandma Sun

124
00:07:46,200 --> 00:07:49,560
she somewhat grasps what the baby means

125
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:51,000
It seems

126
00:07:51,280 --> 00:07:53,560
there's something wrong with the house

127
00:07:54,520 --> 00:07:56,120
But what exactly it is

128
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,520
she said she doesn't know either

129
00:08:00,280 --> 00:08:01,000
Old Wang

130
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:04,120
A little spirit being stuck where it died

131
00:08:04,200 --> 00:08:05,160
I get that

132
00:08:05,400 --> 00:08:07,920
And I get he's attached to Grandma Sun

133
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:10,240
But they belong to different worlds

134
00:08:10,400 --> 00:08:12,080
Grandma Sun didn't actively keep him

135
00:08:12,440 --> 00:08:13,920
So why this bond with her?

136
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:16,560
Her time is running out

137
00:08:17,440 --> 00:08:18,680
Birth, age, sickness, death

138
00:08:19,320 --> 00:08:20,560
is the natural way of things

139
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:26,040
Right now, only sending that child

140
00:08:26,320 --> 00:08:27,760
away

141
00:08:27,960 --> 00:08:29,480
is what's best for both of them

142
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:35,559
To send the little one off

143
00:08:35,760 --> 00:08:37,559
we need to know his grievance

144
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,600
The house is bad

145
00:08:40,880 --> 00:08:42,240
But why?

146
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:50,400
Let the child switch places with me

147
00:08:50,400 --> 00:08:51,440
That might just... No way

148
00:08:54,280 --> 00:08:54,960
Old Wang

149
00:08:55,520 --> 00:08:57,080
The only one who knows what's wrong

150
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:58,040
is that child

151
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:58,960
If we drag this out any longer

152
00:08:59,120 --> 00:08:59,760
Xiaobai

153
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:00,600
and the baby in her belly

154
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:01,560
will be in even greater danger

155
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:03,040
Still, no way

156
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:04,880
I'll go

157
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:06,760
At worst, I'll just rest in bed longer

158
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:07,840
I won't allow it

159
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:09,280
But two lives are at stake!

160
00:09:09,680 --> 00:09:10,560
Besides

161
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:12,120
I've still got Lin You

162
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:19,040
No

163
00:09:21,400 --> 00:09:22,760
If we send the child away

164
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:25,480
Grandma Sun will have nothing left

165
00:09:34,400 --> 00:09:35,120
Lin You

166
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,120
Actually

167
00:09:38,760 --> 00:09:40,160
Grandma Sun still has us

168
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:43,000
You kids really are something

169
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:44,160
Here's the plan

170
00:09:44,640 --> 00:09:46,240
Come back to Daji with me to grab things

171
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:46,920
Alright

172
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:48,360
Got it

173
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:58,600
Let's go

174
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:10,120
Uncle Wang

175
00:10:10,680 --> 00:10:11,800
Liuliu took Grandma out

176
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:13,760
Good

177
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,440
Then let's get started

178
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:19,200
Kid

179
00:10:19,400 --> 00:10:20,320
Always ready

180
00:10:23,640 --> 00:10:24,480
Zhou Yi

181
00:10:25,760 --> 00:10:27,280
Don't try to be a hero

182
00:10:27,800 --> 00:10:29,720
Just follow my lead

183
00:10:30,160 --> 00:10:31,440
Got it, Old Wang

184
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,480
Hurry up already

185
00:10:45,280 --> 00:10:46,360
By the urgent decree!

186
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:47,080
Enter!

187
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:15,560
Kid

188
00:11:15,800 --> 00:11:16,320
Hurry

189
00:11:19,680 --> 00:11:20,240
Zhou Yi

190
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:23,440
Are you okay?

191
00:11:26,280 --> 00:11:27,120
Just now

192
00:11:28,160 --> 00:11:29,760
I was itching all over

193
00:11:30,400 --> 00:11:31,480
I couldn't breathe

194
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:33,680
I felt like

195
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:36,640
I was about to suffocate

196
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:53,280
Kid

197
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:55,240
Call Liuliu

198
00:11:55,520 --> 00:11:57,080
Tell her to bring Grandma back

199
00:11:57,640 --> 00:11:59,240
We'll take Zhou Yi back first

200
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:00,280
Tomorrow morning

201
00:12:00,800 --> 00:12:02,640
come with me to Xiaobai's place

202
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:03,880
Got it

203
00:12:04,960 --> 00:12:05,480
Zhou Yi

204
00:12:05,640 --> 00:12:06,200
It's okay

205
00:12:06,440 --> 00:12:07,320
Master is here

206
00:12:16,760 --> 00:12:17,280
Uncle Wang

207
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:18,880
I've been asking the whole way

208
00:12:18,880 --> 00:12:20,080
and you haven't said a thing

209
00:12:20,560 --> 00:12:21,920
What's really going on here?

210
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:25,320
No wonder Zhou Yi ended up like that

211
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:27,640
Xiaobai's house really does have issues

212
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:29,640
But...

213
00:12:30,120 --> 00:12:31,520
we've never seen anything

214
00:12:31,520 --> 00:12:32,720
quite like Zhou Yi's case before

215
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:35,720
A baby's body

216
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:37,360
can't compare to an adult's

217
00:12:41,680 --> 00:12:42,880
Just because it's fine now

218
00:12:43,160 --> 00:12:44,920
doesn't mean it was fine before

219
00:12:45,640 --> 00:12:46,880
At the end of the day

220
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:48,480
it's not really the house's problem

221
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,280
It's the human heart

222
00:12:50,560 --> 00:12:51,440
that's gone wrong

223
00:13:10,800 --> 00:13:11,600
Uncle Wang

224
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:13,280
Will what we're doing

225
00:13:13,720 --> 00:13:15,120
actually punish the wicked?

226
00:13:16,880 --> 00:13:19,040
When a man does evil

227
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:20,760
he can't hide it from heaven and earth

228
00:13:20,800 --> 00:13:22,120
nor from himself

229
00:13:22,560 --> 00:13:23,960
Evil done in the open

230
00:13:23,960 --> 00:13:25,240
won't be tolerated by the law

231
00:13:25,440 --> 00:13:26,800
Evil done in the shadows

232
00:13:26,880 --> 00:13:28,360
won't be tolerated by gods or ghosts

233
00:13:29,320 --> 00:13:31,080
Go for it, kid

234
00:13:31,520 --> 00:13:33,400
Just do as I taught you
